SO I THINK THEY PURPOSEFULLY

28:57.100 --> 29:02.067
PUT IT WITHIN A WOODED AREA

29:02.067 --> 29:03.767
OUTSIDE OF THE PUBLIC'S VIEW.

29:03.767 --> 29:07.767
**

