IF YOU DON'T KNOW WHERE THE CAVE

30:00.500 --> 30:03.500
IS, YOU WON'T FIND IT.

30:03.500 --> 30:07.300
I MEAN, I WAS BORN AND RAISED

30:03.500 --> 30:07.300
RIGHT BY IT AND NEVER KNEW

30:07.300 --> 30:08.667
THAT CAVE WAS THERE

30:08.667 --> 30:10.300
UNTIL PROBABLY 10 YEARS AGO,

30:10.300 --> 30:13.167
SO THAT'S HOW OFF

30:10.300 --> 30:13.167
AND HIDDEN IT IS.

