OKAY.

33:47.067 --> 33:48.700
I THINK, THIS TIME,

33:47.067 --> 33:48.700
MY ADRENALINE

33:48.700 --> 33:49.967
WAS PUMPING A LITTLE MORE.

33:49.967 --> 33:51.867
IT'S EXCITING TO WALK

33:49.967 --> 33:51.867
THROUGH WOODS, YOU KNOW,

33:51.867 --> 33:55.367
WITH A FLASHLIGHT WITH YOU

33:51.867 --> 33:55.367
AFTER THE PARK'S CLOSED.

33:55.367 --> 33:59.833
AT THIS POINT, WE SHOULD

33:55.367 --> 33:59.833
NOT HAVE BEEN THERE.

