I'M EVEN MORE EXCITED TO GO BACK

33:59.833 --> 34:04.600
BECAUSE NOW WE HAVE FLASHLIGHTS.

34:04.600 --> 34:07.833
WE CAN SEE INSIDE THE CAVE

34:04.600 --> 34:07.833
AND FIGURE OUT WHAT THAT NOISE

34:07.833 --> 34:09.367
WAS THAT WE INITIALLY HEARD.

