THE ONLY WAY TO DO THAT

34:09.367 --> 34:12.367
WAS TO GO INTO THE CAVE

34:12.367 --> 34:14.267
AND TO GET A GOOD LOOK

34:12.367 --> 34:14.267
AT EVERYTHING.

