THE FLASHLIGHTS WEREN'T

34:36.767 --> 34:38.167
STRONG ENOUGH

34:38.167 --> 34:40.433
TO BE ABLE TO FULLY ILLUMINATE

34:38.167 --> 34:40.433
THE CAVE,

34:40.433 --> 34:44.367
SO WE SLOWLY KEPT MOVING

34:40.433 --> 34:44.367
CLOSER AND CLOSER.

34:44.367 --> 34:50.267
**

34:50.267 --> 34:51.867
YOU KNOW WHEN YOU HAVE

34:50.267 --> 34:51.867
SOMETHING TELL YOU,

34:51.867 --> 34:55.300
"DON'T DO IT,"

34:51.867 --> 34:55.300
BUT YOU STILL WANT TO DO IT?

34:55.300 --> 34:56.800
WELL, THAT'S WHAT

34:55.300 --> 34:56.800
HAPPENED TO US.

34:56.800 --> 34:59.367
**

